name: Eetween peace and reason
description: Marins x Itaguaré Crossing, Serra da Mantiqueira - MG, 2017 - Whenever I need advice to make sense of things hammering in my mind, I try to go to the nearest mountain, clear my head, and listen to the winds telling me which directions to take. The noise of the big city interferes a lot with this connection between man and nature - 4608x3456 px - 300 ppi - TRACKLANDCo.
